<P><HI>LONDON,</HI> Printed by <HI>J. Streater,</HI> for <HI>Henry Twiford, George Sawbridge, Th<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 letter"></HI> and <HI>John Place,</HI> and are to be &s;old at their Shops, 1657</P>
